text: They are the modelling siblings who are the offspring of catwalk royalty and nineties supermodel Cindy Crawford. So it's no surprise Kaia Gerber and her brother Presley enjoyed a stylish night out fit for models at Delilah restaurant, in West Hollywood on Friday. The rising star, 17, ran her fingers through her shoulder - length brunette tresses to reveal her good looking features. She's fabulous : Kaia Gerber looked spitting image of her supermodel mum Cindy Crawford as she enjoyed a night out with her brother Presley, in West Hollywood on Friday Keeping the breeze to the evening air off, Kaia nailed an edgy look with her biker chic style leather jacket. Presley sported a khaki green bomber jacket to bring a splash of colour to his all
